room_title: Escape room "Outbreak" by Trapped RGV in Harlingen
room_description: A virus outbreak has quarantined the Midwest Research & Development Facility For Disease Control. A global pandemic is spreading. You must save the world, but the only scientists that can help you have disappeared. To find the cure you must decipher their puzzles and find the clues left behind to escape before the virus spreads and the lab melts down!
